    "A": {name:"Stronghold", desc:"<ul class=\"desc-list\"><li class=\"desc-green\">Upper level is Ceiling and Vantage terrain.</li><li class=\"desc-green\">Door is Accessible and Heavy terrain.</li><li class=\"desc-green\">The three barrels are Blocking and Heavy terrain.</li><li class=\"desc-green\">Small broken ramparts on the edge of the Vantage terrain are Insignificant and Exposed terrain.</li><li class=\"desc-green\">All other parts of it are Heavy terrain.</li><li class=\"desc-green\">For the purposes of control range, ignore the door and parts of this terrain feature less than 2\" high when determining visibility.</li><li class=\"desc-green\">Cover.</li><li class=\"desc-green\">Obscured.</li></ul>"},
